name: Gloces
description:
Introduction

This is a narrow limestone canyon, as narrow as some of the slots in Utah. Unlike Utah canyons, this one has running water, mossy walls and hanging ferns, especially in Spring and Early summer. Some sections of the canyon are so deep that sunlight barely penetrates.
